                "invention-title": [
                    "Negative electrode and battery using same",
                    "一种负极及应用其的电池"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides a negative electrode and a battery using the same, the negative electrode comprises a composite silicon-based material, and the composite silicon-based material comprises a silicon-based material as an inner core and poly (1-chloroheptafluorocyclopentene) as a coating layer. The poly (1-chloroheptafluorocyclopentene) is introduced to coat the silicon-based material, so that the loss of active lithium can be reduced, the energy density can be improved, and the poly (1-chloroheptafluorocyclopentene) can be used as a buffer layer in the expansion and shrinkage process of the silicon-based material to prevent the SEI film from cracking. Moreover, a plurality of fluorine groups are provided to form hydrogen bonds with hydroxyl groups on the surface of the silicon-based material, so that the stability of the SEI film in the expansion process of the silicon-based negative electrode material is improved, and the cycle performance and the first coulombic efficiency of the battery are further improved. And on the other hand, the poly (1-chloroheptafluorocyclopentene) as the coating layer, provided F, Cl and cyclopentene play a role in coordination, and guarantee can be provided for the safety of the battery cell."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提供一种负极及应用其的电池，该负极包括复合硅基材料，复合硅基材料包括作为内核的硅基材料、作为包覆层的聚1‑氯七氟环戊烯。本发明通过引入聚1‑氯七氟环戊烯包覆硅基材料，不仅能够减少活性锂损失，提升能量密度，还可以在硅基材料膨胀收缩过程中作为缓冲层并防止SEI膜破裂。并且，通过提供多个氟基团与硅基材料表面羟基形成氢键，提高SEI膜在硅基负极材料膨胀过程中的稳定性，进一步提高电池的循环性能与首次库伦效率。另一方面，作为包覆层的聚1‑氯七氟环戊烯，所提供的F、Cl、环戊烯三者起到协调作用，能够提，为电芯安全提供保障。"
                }
            ]
